image_analysis.ai_description: A black matte-finish cable machine attachment with a textured grip surface featuring two large circular hand holes. The handle has a sleek, modern design with silver metal components including a central U-bolt attachment point secured with a bolt. The product is shown both isolated on a white surface and in use, where a person grips it with both hands connected to a cable machine via a metal carabiner. The packaging highlights it as a universal attachment point that easily connects to any cable machine.
